The paper focuses on robotic reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of CycleGAN for pixel-level image translation suggests a focus on computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of model-based RL algorithms, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper addresses the challenge of reducing human burden in defining tasks and resetting environments, which is relevant to systems and control (cs.SY).
